					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Welcome to the <em>formal</em> beginning of the timeline I'm building with <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/9volt" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2800867&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1530297735" alt="9Volt" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2800867)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/9volt" >9Volt</a></span> and a few others. You can start on 9volt's stuff <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/faster-than-light-prelude">here</a>. This whole setting that we're doing takes place after <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/amnesticization">Team Fuhgeddaboutit</a>'s doomsday, but it's not necessary to read that stuff unless you want a really in-depth look at what happened to the world.</p> <p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/varaxous" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2433554&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1530297735" alt="Varaxous" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2433554)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/varaxous" >Varaxous</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/9volt" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2800867&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1530297735" alt="9Volt" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2800867)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/9volt" >9Volt</a></span> for feedback.</p> 
